headline: Large-cap biotech is a sector to watch for investors: Analysts

headline: HSBC Upgrades Eli Lilly (LLY) to Hold, Lifts Price Target to $700
summary: Eli Lilly and Company (NYSE:LLY) is one of the best stocks for a 20-year long-term stock portfolio. Eli Lilly has substantially underperformed this year with YTD decline of over 5%.
